            <div type="column">
                
                <head type="main">A GENTLE HINT.</head>
                
                <p>In most of the New York shop windows, one reads: "Here we speak French;" "Here we speak Spanish;" "Here we speak German;" "Here we speak Italian." I suggest an improvement&#8212;"Here we speak the <hi rend="italic">Truth</hi>."</p>
                
                <byline>FANNY FERN.</byline>
